      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration experts! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for your next big project. While it is currently in poor condition and will require a dedicated hand to get it back in top shape, it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to build their dream ride from the ground up. If you're ready to roll up your sleeves and breathe new life into a classic, this is the one for you!",
