    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including large dents, heavy paint oxidation, and visible rust on several panels. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission is slipping, requiring immediate professional attention. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest significant time and money into repairs if you intend to make this roadworthy.",
