      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly museum-quality vehicle. This exceptional example remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of care that is seldom seen. The exterior finish retains its original factory luster, while the interior remains flawless, offering a cabin experience that feels entirely untouched. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically perfect, this collector-grade car represents the gold standard for its model. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands as a testament to automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
